| `bmorphism/` | 406 | 100% (across original + backfill) |
| `plurigrid/` | 586 | 100% (across original + backfill) |
| Third-party | 131 | 100% (backfill chunks 1-4) |
| **Total** | **1,244** | **100%** |
\stopverb}
}

